template(name="about")
  .container
    .row.clearfix
      .col-md-6.column
        +voteForMe

        h1 Motivation
        p Because our community hold MLDM Monday event (MLDM stands for Machine Learning and Data Mining) every week in Taipei, 
          | some of events were in tutorial forms. In those tutorial events, 
          | we found the most difficult thing which barriered students to hands on the programs is 
          | the environment synchronization! 
        i Some codes could be executed in teacher's computer, but could not in student's. 
        p Fortunately, we meet docker ......

        h1 Technologies in this project ... 
        ul
          li
            h3 
              a(href="https://www.docker.com/") Docker
          li  
            h3 
              a(href="https://www.meteor.com/") Meteor
          li
            h3 
              a(href="https://github.com/apocas/dockerode") dockerode
          li  
            h3 
              a(href="https://cloud.google.com/compute/") Google Computer Engine
        
        
      .col-md-6.column
        
        h1 Dockerfiles in this project ... 
        ul
          li 
            h3 
              a(target="_blank",href="https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/c3h3/oblas-py278-shogun-ipynb/") c3h3/oblas-py278-shogun-ipynb
            p (used in Try IPyNB)
          li 
            h3 
              a(target="_blank",href="https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/rocker/rstudio/") rocker/rstudio
            p (used in Try RStudio)

          li 
            h3 
              a(target="_blank",href="https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/c3h3/learning-shogun") c3h3/learning-shogun
            p (used in learning shogun)

          li 
            h3 
              a(target="_blank",href="https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/c3h3/dsc2014tutorial") c3h3/dsc2014tutorial
            p (used in DSC2014Tutorial Series)

